ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg&h=6108e080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇唔到你條皮帶係咪完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你搵支電筒照下條嘢有無批口<br />\n對上嗰次幾時換皮帶？"},{"pid":"5f8a7583719df8914c3b80134191c0f403947e7f","tid":323534,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的 前排買左架二手車 <br />\n我就新手P牌仔咩都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁架車開冷氣既情況下慢車同踏Break停車會有吱吱聲<br />\n唔開冷氣就無事既 <br />\n<br />\n同埋試過幾次D波踏break等燈等成 死火 <br />\n雖則撻得返著但個人都驚驚地 <br />\n<br />\n想問下有無巴打知咩事危唔危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下wd40噴皮帶？著住車，少少咁噴就ok</blockquote><br />\n係咪皮帶唔順 會影響到曬冷氣 同死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試試轉頭 但可能我連皮帶係咩位都要搵下<br />\n完全唔熟車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺副engine ，冷氣泵附近<br />\n你會見到有一條或者兩條皮帶<br />\n睇下有無蝕或者撕左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg&h=6108e080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇唔到你條皮帶係咪完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你搵