/>\n對上嗰次幾時換皮帶？</blockquote><br />\n賣車個個話 車房前排ZIP完皮帶</blockquote><br />\n相既最右面好似見到皮帶"},{"pid":"073ba9911f03eaac28d8aa5aad479e24de8ba6c7","tid":323534,"uid":41784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會死火，著冷氣有怪聲，應該係冇Power steering fluid<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識點加，自己google</blockquote><br />\n Jazz電軚冇得加軚油<br />\n另外請問上巴打點解話wd40噴皮帶係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130120f33fc151047c3554a801ee66212c98a241","tid":323534,"uid":52542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會死火，著冷氣有怪聲，應該係冇Power steering fluid<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識點加，自己google</blockquote><br />\n Jazz電軚冇得加軚油<br />\n另外請問上巴打點解話wd40噴皮帶係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n噴完你架車就gg"},{"pid":"03feb3fb6b7b9448a5182b5169b851d6139737e4","tid":323534,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n試下wd40噴皮帶？著住車，少少咁噴就ok</blockquote><br />\n係咪皮帶唔順 會影響到曬冷氣 同死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試試轉頭 但可能我連皮帶係咩位都要搵下<br />\n完全唔熟車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺副engine ，冷氣泵附近<br />\n你會見到有一條或者兩條皮帶<br />\n睇下有無蝕或者撕左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg&h=6108e080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇唔到你條皮帶係咪完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你搵支電筒照下條嘢有無批口<br />\n對上嗰次幾時換皮帶？</blockquote><br />\n賣車個個話 車房前排ZIP完皮帶</blockquote><br />\n相既最右面好似見到皮帶</blockquote><br />\n巴打介唔介意圈圈<br />\n其實我岩岩望住發覺乜都唔識望唔出啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家都應該諗住去車房睇睇架喇"},{"pid":"666487760b63f1c3db39ec5ae2eb5a1fbf8a79db","tid":323534,"uid":29447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:35:05.000Z","msg":"我嗰部都係咁<br />\n架車開冷氣+低轉時就吱吱聲<br />\n尤其喺停車場踩住brake落斜就嘈到仆街<br />\n<br />\n啱啱去完車房換左皮帶同皮帶轆<br />\n條舊皮帶甩皮，個舊轆有虛位<br />\n<br />\n換完一開車即時靜哂<br />\n低轉時有力左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb85bf99ffd17bccc4c04e29317803957f03e89","tid":323534,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會死火，著冷氣有怪聲，應該係冇Power steering fluid<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識點加，自己google</blockquote><br />\n Jazz電軚冇得加軚油<br />\n另外請問上巴打點解話wd40噴皮帶係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能會靜一陣，之後又響翻<br />\n同埋皮帶俾油浸過會更快打柴"},{"pid":"941def46afeebd9afef1b2eee5bee079fb754572","tid":323534,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n係咪皮帶唔順 會影響到曬冷氣 同死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我試試轉頭 但可能我連皮帶係咩位都要搵下<br />\n完全唔熟車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺副engine ，冷氣泵附近<br />\n你會見到有一條或者兩條皮帶<br />\n睇下有無蝕或者撕左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F165208_31d7a1fe7e780dabfd138a6dc9794bc1.jpg&h=6108e080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇唔到你條皮帶係咪完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你搵支電筒照下條嘢有無批口<br />\n對上嗰次幾時換皮帶？</blockquote><br />\n賣車個個話 車房前排ZIP完皮帶</blockquote><br />\n相既最右面好似見到皮帶</blockquote><br />\n巴打介唔介意圈圈<br />\n其實我岩岩望住發覺乜都唔識望唔出啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家都應該諗住去車房睇睇架喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/c29230043/1452251851-543935306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fc29230043%2F1452251851-543935306.jpg&h=b5147314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右面都唔似皮帶<br />\n張相就係皮帶啦，你應該見到<br />\n之前我靜車起步通常都係勁嘈，比車房一睇，就話皮帶鬆左"},{"pid":"efc4016812b7ec30d6bf27dff705c8ee11130c3c","tid":323534,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嗰部都係咁<br />\n架車開冷氣+低轉時就吱吱聲<br />\n尤其喺停車場踩住brake落斜就嘈到仆街<br />\n<br />\n啱啱去完車房換左皮帶同皮帶轆<br />\n條舊皮帶甩皮，個舊轆有虛位<br />\n<br />\n換完一開車即時靜哂<br />\n低轉時有力左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打知唔知如果皮帶問題會唔會引申到<br />\n我D波停車太耐有時會死火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}